{"tid":1160462,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有玩健身想進步既人就入啦","createTime":"2019-05-18T13:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T18:52:33.000Z","uid":180114,"like":15,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"31377c604fbed724c455eb2e89fb5678110f0f2f","tid":1160462,"uid":180114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T13:12:29.000Z","msg":"建議你地玩多啲SBD<br />\n<br />\nSBD係乜？<br />\n姐係卧推硬拉深蹲<br />\n<br />\n依三樣訓練涉及好多組肌肉一齊training<br />\n<br />\n令你地進步得更快，學好依三樣基本動作，其他machine你唔會唔識做<br />\n<br />\n唔好話做三個動作驚傷，基本做得正確，就唔會傷，你做傷自己，都係自己一直做錯<br />\n<br />\n最後都係個句想進步，無論增肌定減脂都要有各方面佩合"},{"pid":"2b225ec3ab488642d2b71931f5eb0278ee3162d8","tid":1160462,"uid":13350,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T13:19:11.000Z","msg":"同埋要做ohp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43313491e8c56ae2f016dff45751ea1e8b77b95a","tid":1160462,"uid":217433,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T13:27:34.000Z","msg":"但唔夠functional喎"},{"pid":"7dda7b4bbe13fb1d83de47be1c939f77fc9b3ccb","tid":1160462,"uid":28845,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T14:06:20.000Z","msg":"硬拉深蹲真係驚整傷背脊，冇人親身教真係唔敢自己亂黎。<br />\n操腳背都係做gym 入面啲機算"},{"pid":"c69275742756de249382d1923d33ae3f0b05e29c","tid":1160462,"uid":142359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T14:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e922a2fb75dc72b01c3ab2ee7b463287ae41c0","tid":1160462,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"7dda7b4bbe13fb1d83de47be1c939f77fc9b3ccb","tid":1160462,"uid":28845,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T14:06:20.000Z","msg":"硬拉深蹲真係驚整傷背脊，冇人親身教真係唔敢自己亂黎。<br />\n操腳背都係做gym 入面啲機算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T14:09:39.000Z","msg":"保持腰直就得<br />\n一開始唔洗重<br />\n吉bar練動作先"},{"pid":"22c6dcffbb51167be5d5c9ecb011dcce6ba36332","tid":1160462,"uid":161190,"like":0,"dislike